{"tid":2060493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【612訪問重溫】林鄭落淚：話我「賣港」？我點樣去賣港？","createTime":"2020-06-11T16:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T05:10:50.000Z","uid":24660,"like":9,"dislike":313,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"e17354c1a3579e0cb3f9f344a15e5b727b55abf4","tid":2060493,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T16:30:19.000Z","msg":"【林鄭月娥無綫專訪】林鄭月娥哽咽否認賣港 無因推動修例感心虛<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥接受無綫電視獨家專訪，其間一度哽咽，提及有人批評她賣港時，反問她怎樣賣港。被問到市民要求她下台，有無想過做的事是否正確，林鄭月娥說，從來沒有因為推動修訂《逃犯條例》一事感到心虛。<br />\n<br />\n她在訪問中說，在香港土生土長，跟所有香港人一同成長，對這個地方的愛，令她作出了不少個人犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，家中有一名不理政事的丈夫，丈夫曾反問，她怎可能賣港，認為她是做行政長官後，賣身給香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2937153022969163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2937153022969163&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0p2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=ca36e540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2937153022969163</a>"},{"pid":"a61fee75ff2f6e7bec48d12e5bf8eab001ca6bd0","tid":2060493,"uid":22436,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T16:31:29.000Z","msg":"林奠而家喜迎國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f7782d3b6433f6512b39dade4e424813ee9096","tid":2060493,"uid":24660,"like":4,"dislike":63,"score":-59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image1.thenewslens.com/2019/6/chijx5u3ycishrlzd3528d22vcdsc3.jpg?auto=compress&amp;h=648&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage1.thenewslens.com%2F2019%2F6%2Fchijx5u3ycishrlzd3528d22vcdsc3.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26h%3D648%26q%3D80%26w%3D1080&h=e4c09c78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ef2f28c48b7ec9eb426c93d58cd4fe1a17aea8f","tid":2060493,"uid":24660,"like":1,"dislike":88,"score":-87,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T16:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/66041614_wAo6F_1200x0.png\" dat